name: Kiki - By the sea

reviews.review_text:
Positive things first - the vibe of the place is just really soft and soothing, a perfect place for your family to hangout and have a couple of cocktails. We loved the vibe with really good crowd. It’s in the backwaters so you can experience a really warm breeze coming in instead of sea smell which could be irritating sometimes. The location was perfect in a way to have a good time with your family and friends. Even the food was not that bad. The staff were really nice and humble. Good experience overall.
Feedback - the food is overpriced! We loved the cocktails but the quantity of the food looking at the prices was below average. It’s like 4 small shrimps @1800. It was incredibly small portion like tasting menu instead of food on a plate. I hope they improve it over time as they got a really good ambiance, smooth jazz music, an amazing vibe. Food is where they really need to focus on. I don’t remember the pricing of cocktails but I am pretty confident everything was overpriced from my experience. At the end of the it’s Goa - unnecessary overpriced.

Kiki-By the Sea in Goa is an amazing spot right by the ocean. The view is breathtaking, and the vibe is super cozy and welcoming. They have a great mix of dishes from around the world, with fresh seafood being a standout. Their cocktails are also really tasty. The staff is super friendly and always ready to help. Whether you're on a date, with family, or hanging out with friends, it's a fantastic place to enjoy a meal. Definitely check it out!

A beautiful place to spend the entire afternoon till the evening. The sunsets are just beautiful from this place with a lot of sea side tables. The cocktails are  amazing and well made with plenty of in-house options to choose from. The food is their crow jewel, with an ample amount of options and decent portion sizes. We were very happy with the service and how warm the staff is, especially Arup, who hosted us and deserves a special mention in this review. If you're in Goa and want delicious food with an amazing ambience, it's a must to visit Kiki- By the sea.

description:
### Kiki - By the Sea: A Dining Gem Nestled in Corlim

Tucked away in the picturesque Corlim Industrial Estate, **Kiki - By the Sea** boasts a commendable rating of **4.2** based on **3,448 reviews**, making it a go-to spot for locals and tourists alike. Guests frequently mention the restaurant's charm through tags such as **"cover charge"** (156 mentions), **"cocktails"** (105), **"sunset"** (74), and **"shravan"** (43), highlighting its well-rounded offerings that cater to diverse tastes and experiences.

### Ambiance & Design

The moment you step into Kiki - By the Sea, you are enveloped by a soft and calming ambiance that sets a perfect stage for a family outing or a cozy dinner with friends. Reviewers consistently praise the blend of modern and coastal décor, enhanced by soothing **smooth jazz music** wafting through the air. The outdoor seating areas are adorned with comfy arrangements, providing stunning views of shimmering backwaters and the enticing hues of sunset. Captured in a customer-provided photo, the lanterns adorning the tables and the lush surrounding greenery create a warm and inviting atmosphere perfect for lasting memories.

### Menu & Culinary Experience

Kiki's culinary offerings are a delight, particularly its **fresh seafood**, which is often referred to as the **"crow jewel"** of the menu. Patrons rave about the various dishes, showcasing a wide array of global options that cater to different palates. Signature cocktails are another highlight, crafted with precision and featuring plenty of **in-house options**. However, feedback regarding portion sizes presents a mixed bag, with some diners expressing that the **food may be overpriced** for the quantity served, with one reviewer noting an instance of only **four small shrimp** being offered for a hefty price. Here, the restaurant seems to straddle the line of culinary delight and value, leaving an opportunity for improvement to meet the high expectations that a venue of this caliber garners.

### Customer Experience & Service

Service at Kiki is a consistent point of praise, with staff described as **"friendly"** and ever-ready to assist. Reviewers have pointed out the hospitality of team members, with **Arup** receiving special recognition for his warmth and attentiveness. Customers feel well cared for, enhancing the overall dining experience. Reservations appear to be recommended, especially during peak hours when sunset views are most sought after, ensuring that your spot is secured in this popular destination.

### Popularity & Reviews

The social media buzz surrounding Kiki reflects its vibrant atmosphere and culinary options, with many urging friends to make it a must-visit during any trip to Goa. The restaurant's picturesque sunset views paired with its flavorful cocktails provide a memorable backdrop, echoed throughout customer reviews. The consistent mention of the ambiance and the mix of international dishes underlines Kiki's place as a beloved hotspot.

### Utilizing Visual Content

Imagery from patrons offers a visual narrative that complements the dining experience at Kiki. The photos depict not only the nicely arranged tables with coastal views but also vibrant cocktails that beckon for a taste. Reviewers have captured the essence of Kiki, focusing on the inviting setup and beautiful sunset settings that elevate every meal into a memorable occasion.

In summary, Kiki - By the Sea stands out as a restaurant that combines stunning views, delightful cocktails, and a welcoming atmosphere. While its culinary offerings may have room for growth in terms of portion size and value, the overall experience remains highly regarded, making it a recommended stop for anyone looking to savour the flavors of Goa while enjoying the serene coastal backdrop.
